{"tid":334253,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[網頁遊戲] agar.io","createTime":"2017-07-24T14:09:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-23T15:51:11.000Z","uid":56875,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"afb0947873534cd3825340ded31e4ed81921b848","tid":334253,"uid":56875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T14:09:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://agar.io/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fagar.io%2F&d=786xU7PnK6mKZu4gmYOL3SwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=b3370015\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://agar.io/</a><br />\n請選FFA mode<br />\n玩East Asia <br />\n<br />\n因為入去係隨機分配SERVER，所以你入到去見到排行榜成堆韓撚名就岩，唔岩就F5再入。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/24/220633_a19ddbe22afc139c538bfca41cea40ad.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F24%2F220633_a19ddbe22afc139c538bfca41cea40ad.png&h=9fb60556&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n麻煩各位巴絲打係前面加[HKG]，方便相認同唔好食自己友，一齊合作上頭十名。<br />\n<br />\n我個遊戲名[HKG] 食屎大<br />\n<br />\n幫推POST<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  THX!!!<br />\n<br />\n引用：<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/Agar.io\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FAgar.io&d=786xU7PnK6mKZu4gmYOL3SwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=544d6689\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/Agar.io</a><br />\n《<a href=\"http://Agar.io\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FAgar.io&d=786xU7PnK6mKZu4gmYOL3SwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=610be13a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Agar.io</a>》是M28推出的一款大型多人線上遊戲。<br />\n在遊戲中玩家控制自己的圓形，並擊殺質量比自身小的圓形為最終目的。<br />\n<br />\n基本上就是大球吃小球的遊戲，由於小球速度永遠比大球來的快，所以大球要利用空白鍵才比較容易吃掉小球<br />\n但分裂的風險很高，有可能分裂前無法吃掉你的敵人就變成能吞掉你。<br />\n<br />\n基本操作<br />\n游標：控制球的移動方向　W：朝移動方向吐出小球　空白鍵：朝移動方向分裂<br />\n質量需要超過（35）才能吐出小球及進行分裂<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n引用：<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=28462&amp;snA=169\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D28462%26snA%3D169&d=786xU7PnK6mKZu4gmYOL3SwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=31e4a1ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=28462&amp;snA=169</a><br />\nＷ：吐出小球<br />\n主要功用為彈射出綠刺球：<br />\n吐出小球所耗損的質量會隨自身質量而增加．而吐出的質量會比自身耗損的質量減少15%-20%<br />\n當小球停下後質量會再 -1 ．同時有機會成為重生玩家的球<br />\nＥＸ：質量為５４的球吐出小球損耗１７．彈射出去的球質量只有１４．停下來為１３<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n空白鍵：分裂<br />\n將自身一半質量彈射出去．分裂並不會造成質量耗損．分裂上限為１６顆．也就是空白鍵４次<br />\n分裂後需要經過一段冷卻期才能重新合拼<br />\nＥＸ：質量為１０００的球分裂後各為５００<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n彩色點點<br />\n彩色點點遍佈在整個場上．每顆質量（平均為１）．前期皆為吃彩點來增加質量．<br />\n而彩色點點會不斷生成．所以並不會有吃完的情況"},{"pid":"5ae88cfbc277e199e20e358e98cf606624ba2f7d","tid":334253,"uid":56875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T14:11:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a1d799b43a39586ba51092c16e92223a47bce08","tid":334253,"uid":128223,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T14:12:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"335588b59cea5a2c38c53a99c1dd70e70e4c1fc2","tid":334253,"uid":56875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T14:13:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>潮流</blockquote><br />\n復古<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6b7e22531f63f5f97540a5ac00060e051d053f4","tid":334253,"uid":63202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T14:14:04.000Z","msg":"記得以前同個巴屌打圍威威既高登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6c84a5212838e2f5881686fa00bdba3857c18e6","tid":334253,"uid":9125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T14:14:41.000Z","msg":"以前一推出嗰陣晚晚玩 同幾個老死組隊由零一齊食到上頭3，玩贏韓仔台仔，回憶總是美好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"775a97ee36373befea3c79e55850064dfbc4b047","tid":334253,"uid":56875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T14